MALACAÑANG RESIDENCE OF THE PRESIDENT OF THE PHILIPPINES MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 297

RESERVING FOR PLAYGROUND PURPOSES A CERTAIN PARCEL OF THE PRIVATE DOMAIN OF THE GOVERNMENT, SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF MABINI, PROVINCE OF DAVAO.

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of General Services, and pursuant to the provisions of Section 64 (e) of the Revised Administrative Code in relation to Section 1 of Republic Act No. 477, I, FERDINAND E. MARCOS, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale or settlement and reserve for playground purposes under the administration of the Municipality of Mabini, subject to private rights, if any there be, the following parcel of the private domain, situated in the Municipality of Mabini, and more particularly described as follows:

Block 2, Psd-46341

(Playground site)

A parcel of land (Block 2 of the subdivision plan Psd-46341, being, a portion of Lot 92, Psd-34108), situated in the Municipality of Mabini, Province of Davao, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the NE., points 1-2-3-4-5-6-7, by Road Lot 1; on the SE., points 7-8-9- by Road Lot 1; on the West, points 9-10-11-12-13-14-15-16 by Road Lot 1; and on the NW., points 16-1 by Road Lot 1, all of the subdivision plan. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan, being N. 29 deg. 57’W., 437.30 m. from B.L.L.M. No. 20, Pantukan Cadastre,

